<paragraph blockId="8.[264,1322,1646,1856]" box="[264,1322,1710,1736]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Diagnosis. Four dc, acr absent. Hairs and bristles on thorax brown. Hind tarsomere 1 with</paragraph>
